OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with some bright
OL,6,Fspells at first. Rain will arrive
OL,7,Flater this afternoon with some heavy
OL,8,Fbursts at times and a risk of some
OL,9,Fthundery downpours. Winds picking up
OL,10,Fthrough the day.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain will continue through
OL,13,Fthe evening and first part of the
OL,14,Fnight with heavy downpours at times.
OL,15,FGradually turning drier towards the
OL,16,Fend of the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
